This paper is about biomedical image analysis challenges and the development of a set of recommendations for the reporting of challenges to improve transparency and reproducibility of results. The paper is likely to be categorized under computer vision (cs.CV) as it deals with image analysis, machine learning (cs.LG) as it discusses benchmarking algorithms, artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it proposes a set of recommendations, multimedia (cs.MM) as it deals with biomedical images, and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it aims to improve the interpretability of challenge results.
